{"tid":688714,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[真音樂] IU出演《柳熙烈的寫生簿》400期重大特輯...見證十年不變","createTime":"2018-06-03T12:53:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-04T10:49:03.000Z","uid":34643,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"808015b893f020c321153312ccd8051a6223158d","tid":688714,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T12:53:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/-pTCFDnsHBw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F-pTCFDnsHBw&d=MjM4JMG%2BNWi3m7oXykWPo%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=722136cb\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/-pTCFDnsHBw</a><br />\n<br />\n2日晚，IU出演的音樂訪談類節目《柳熙烈的寫生簿》400期特輯正式播出。IU身穿白色連衣長裙外搭莊重黑色西裝優雅亮相，帶來了《Dear Moon》、《雪人》、《夜信》三首個人熱門歌曲，並榮獲了寫生簿&ldquo;最佳成長獎&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n因為行程超級繁忙而提前三個月預約了本期節目的出演邀請，作為今年上半年繁忙工作的句點。柳熙烈為IU頒發&ldquo;最佳成長獎&rdquo;，9年間獨自茁壯成長，成為了優秀的音樂人，使見證你初始的我們十分幸福，特授予此獎。<br />\n<br />\n在這樣慢節奏的節目裡，聽著IU關於音樂和生活的故事，感受治愈的力量！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=37dAtN6iexs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D37dAtN6iexs&d=MjM4JMG%2BNWi3m7oXykWPo%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=e6fe9544\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=37dAtN6iexs</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/9cQDbTOJkbU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F9cQDbTOJkbU&d=MjM4JMG%2BNWi3m7oXykWPo%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=3259347b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/9cQDbTOJkbU</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aKDbh5WO5qE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DaKDbh5WO5qE&d=MjM4JMG%2BNWi3m7oXykWPo%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=e594069b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aKDbh5WO5qE</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20180603/3e689303464c46668e4fe6441cc402ee.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com%2Fimages%2F2018